## Overview

FilmCircle is a **community-based movie review and discovery platform** that replaces traditional star ratings with a 4-option opinion system. Users can search movies (via OMDb/IMDB API), submit structured reviews, discuss films in a community feed, create topic-based clubs, and independently upload their own films — all at zero cost using free-tier cloud services.

**Core innovation**: replacing ambiguous star ratings with four clearly-named categories:
`Skip` · `Considerable` · `Go For It` · `Excellent`

