## Architecture Decision

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    BROWSER (Client)                     │
│         React 18 + Vite · React Router v6               │
│         Chart.js (infographics) · Axios (HTTP)          │
└──────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘
                       │ REST API (JSON)
┌──────────────────────▼──────────────────────────────────┐
│                  Node.js + Express (Server)              │
│  JWT Auth · express-validator · Mongoose ORM            │
│  OMDb Proxy · CORS · Global Error Handler               │
└──────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘
                       │
        ┌──────────────┴───────────────┐
        ▼                              ▼
  MongoDB Atlas                  OMDb API
  (Free M0 Tier)             (Free, 1k req/day)
  Collections:               Movie search + details
  Users, Movies,             Poster, plot, genre,
  Reviews, Posts, Clubs      director, cast, year
```

**Why this stack?**
- **React + Vite**: Fast HMR, modern JSX, component-based — college standard
- **Express**: Lightweight, flexible, massive ecosystem
- **MongoDB**: Flexible schema suits community content; Atlas free tier fits zero-cost requirement
- **OMDb API**: Free, IMDB-backed, no scraping, 1000 req/day sufficient for college project

