## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests

#### Backend (Jest + Supertest)
```bash
cd server
npm test
# Or with coverage report:
npm test -- --coverage
```
Each test file connects to a **separate in-memory MongoDB** using `mongodb-memory-server`:
```bash
npm install --save-dev mongodb-memory-server
```
This ensures tests never touch the production database.

